sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 👤 You
    participant Phone as 📱 Phone App
    participant RBI as 🏛️ RBI Server
    participant Bank as 🏦 Your Bank
    participant Watch as ⌚ Smartwatch
    
    Note over User,Watch: PHASE 1: LOAD e-RUPEE (2-3 seconds, TLS encrypted)
    
    User->>Phone: Opens ZiPPaY, enters ₹500
    Phone->>Phone: Requires biometric (fingerprint/face)
    User->>Phone: Authenticates ✓
    
    Phone->>Phone: Requests OTP (One-Time Password)
    User->>Phone: Enters OTP from email ✓
    
    Phone->>RBI: Sends encrypted request (TLS 1.3)
    Note over Phone,RBI: {user_id, amount: 500, 2FA_verified}
    
    RBI->>Bank: Queries balance = ₹10,000? ✓
    Bank-->>RBI: Verified ✓
    
    RBI->>RBI: Generates e-Rupee Token (RBI-issued digital currency)
    Note over RBI: {TokenID:UUID, Amount:500, Timestamp, Nonce}
    
    RBI->>RBI: Signs token with RBI Private Key (ECDSA-P256)
    RBI->>RBI: Encrypts with Watch Public Key (AES-256)
    
    RBI-->>Phone: Returns encrypted token (TLS 1.3)
    
    Phone->>Watch: BLE handshake (Bluetooth Low Energy)
    Note over Phone,Watch: Negotiate session cipher & keys
    
    Phone->>Watch: Establish encrypted BLE (ECDH key exchange)
    Phone->>Watch: Send encrypted e-Rupee token
    Note over Phone,Watch: {Token, RBI_Signature, Timestamp}
    
    Watch->>Watch: Decrypt using Watch Private Key (Secure Element)
    Watch->>Watch: Verify RBI Signature ✓
    Watch->>Watch: Validate Timestamp (±5 min window)
    Watch->>Watch: Store in hardware-backed storage (EAL4+ certified)
    
    Watch->>Watch: Update LocalLedger: balance = ₹500
    Watch->>Watch: Record: TX_LOAD_001 [pending_sync]
    
    Watch-->>User: Display: "✓ ₹500 e-Rupee Loaded"
    Phone-->>User: Shows balance: ₹500
    
    Note over User,Watch: ✓ COMPLETE<br/>Watch holds RBI-backed e-Rupee<br/>Offline capability: 5 transactions max
